headline: Got $5,000? These 3 Growth Stocks Are Trading Near Their 52-Week Lows.
summary: A $5,000 investment can go a long way, especially if you're loading up on fairly cheap stocks that may possess a lot of upside in the long run.  Three potentially excellent growth stocks to buy and hold that are trading near their lows right now include Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD), Amgen (NASDAQ: AMGN), and Prologis (NYSE: PLD).  Advanced Micro Devices, better known as just AMD, is a tech company that possesses a lot of growth opportunities due to artificial intelligence (AI).
